snippet.title: Astronomics Trailer
snippet.description:
Space Exploration meets Asteroid Mining Automation - Build up a faithful crew of bots and command your customizable starship navigating through the asteroid belt full of pseudo employment opportunities so you can save up enough for that ticket to Earth and come home… for the very first time. 

Visit us at http://AstronomicsGame.com
